### ğŸ—ï¸ **Enterprise Module Structure**

```
src/runbooks/
â”œâ”€â”€ ğŸ›ï¸ cfat/                     # Cloud Foundations Assessment Tool
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ assessment/             # Assessment engine and runners
